{"tid":1456834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武先應該走，和理非可以留！counter logic！","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:11.000Z","uid":20948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d477f5a6b7e87d43f389fad97ccfec01ed17cf7","tid":1456834,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:44.000Z","msg":"突然之間一大批鬼AC出現<br />\n一批話走，瘋狂製造白色恐佈<br />\n一批話留，話自己嚇自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本兩邊都有鬼，客觀可達到效果就係最堅定勇武嘅留，和理非怕死嘅走。留低嘅勇武由鬼挑起衝突，一網打盡。失去大批勇武，呢場運動就會急速降溫。<br />\n<br />\n根本應該反其道而行，和理非留係度，乜都唔做，警察吹你唔漲，勇武出返黎睇情況再諗下一步行動。而家搞機場，最撚驚就係政府。諗清楚行動，<br />\n唔好自亂陣腳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97a956369f39adf59e334a4d3097a39f313fe83","tid":1456834,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4dfd1cabd869e002df044e31ffbe0e9df7cb70f1","tid":1456834,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"勇武應該先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8f32fa4819e3a53960afb4edb5831da71cd6a5","tid":1456834,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"同721前晚勁似<br />\n<br />\n好多人屌散水撚 話前線自決<br />\n<br />\n結果721呢? 死傷慘重<br />\n<br />\n由尋晚可見 7月前線已經被滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家一大班分化撚同屌鬼撚就證明上面推論完全正確"},{"pid":"2f104c0cfb8f37175ad35dffea2ebc060cefa6dc","tid":1456834,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8f32fa4819e3a53960afb4edb5831da71cd6a5","tid":1456834,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"同721前晚勁似<br />\n<br />\n好多人屌散水撚 話前線自決<br />\n<br />\n結果721呢? 死傷慘重<br 